{"tid":817081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男童臉部被鐵條貫穿透撿回一命","createTime":"2018-09-13T07:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T09:01:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"48d8748dea5c995c962771ee013da2aa18268603","tid":817081,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180913/640_c78d77f949a83f88d41fd91c7ae2f5d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180913%2F640_c78d77f949a83f88d41fd91c7ae2f5d7.jpg&h=4321b9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國密蘇里州一名男童日前不慎從樹屋摔落，結果被地面一支長30公分的串肉鐵條穿透頭部。神奇的是，這支鐵條沒有傷到任何重要部位，男童可望完全復原。<br />\n <br />\n10歲的康寧漢（Xavier Cunningham）周六在自家樹屋玩耍時，突然被黃蜂攻擊，他驚慌下跌落樹屋，沒想到卻剛好掉在一根尖銳鐵條上，鐵條從他的鼻子左方穿透，尖銳端直接穿出後頸部。<br />\n <br />\n康寧漢嚇得跑回家求救，要媽媽「趕快拔出來」，而他在送醫過程中還不斷哭著說：「我快死了，媽！我感覺得到。」還好這根30公分長的鐵條，奇蹟似「錯過」眼睛、大動脈、腦幹和脊隨，醫師開刀取出鐵條後，康寧漢除了未來聲音可能受影響，其他部位均能完全康復。<br />\n <br />\n負責治療男童的神經外科醫師艾伯索爾（Koji Ebersole）說：「我沒看過異物穿進這麼深的案例中，有人能夠存活下來，更別說他會接近完全復原。」（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180913/640_0eecca8e825a16220da84c50393d0c73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180913%2F640_0eecca8e825a16220da84c50393d0c73.jpg&h=2747c373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180913/640_b896055b5711704af30fe1a8548a1265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180913%2F640_b896055b5711704af30fe1a8548a1265.jpg&h=56b7c067&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"905b49f211958aaf42f7c5bdb864501ac86b2caa","tid":817081,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"大難不死 必有後福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6488c92306e6783d10edfd8ecceb42d64bf8babe","tid":817081,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"命不該絕 捱下世界先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2184e759ad13a5be5302c4699402c9ab526fb245","tid":817081,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"見到都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19229723aa9e03a3273aa6a47eff380db934186c","tid":817081,"uid":34773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"點解有條鐵支"},{"pid":"0db7888f6c45b888781b7f743d5bf2c1643c0bbd","tid":817081,"uid":51436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"咁難先投到胎去美國，唔好咁快死呀"},{"pid":"5414e8e2dc6fa3b24cef0bb5d3b66bf20eb67b30","tid":817081,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6488c92306e6783d10edfd8ecceb42d64bf8babe","tid":817081,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"命不該絕 捱下世界先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"人地係美國人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefb3835dca58c263fa0804da9b7d66529f680a4","tid":817081,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:30:36.000Z","msg":"差果小小就吉穿埋個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e40914a5d4f72cd726d5b619196ffcfc12831d","tid":817081,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚痛"},{"pid":"1c405c796c254b0de01545a4e0a66e3d5edb9b9f","tid":817081,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0